OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow UK sent mentally ill   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpeople back to Caribbean   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of long-term sick and mentally
OL,6, ill people from the Windrush generation
OL,7, were sent back to the Caribbean in what
OL,8, has been described as a "historic      
OL,9, injustice", the BBC has found.         
OL,11,FFormerly classified documents reveal at
OL,12,Fleast 411 people were sent back between
OL,13,Fthe 1950s and the early 1970s, under a 
OL,14,Fscheme that was meant to be voluntary. 
OL,16,FFamilies say they were ripped apart and
OL,17,Fsome were never reunited.              
OL,19,FThe UK government said it was committed
OL,20,Fto tackling the injustices of the era. 
